### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "My first post",
  "userId": 1
}

### Add a comment
POST http://localhost:3000/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "comment": "Nice post!"
}

